{"comments":"MotionEditor — Bounded animation property editing for context menus.\n\n## Design\n\nEdits common animation properties with BOUNDED values only:\n\n- Duration: 0-60000ms (max 1 minute)\n- Delay: 0-10000ms (max 10 seconds)\n- Iterations: 1-1000 (NEVER infinite)\n- Easing: Selection from Schema presets\n- Direction: Normal, Reverse, Alternate\n\n## Safety\n\nThis editor does NOT expose:\n- Infinite iterations (no negative values, no loop:true without bound)\n- Unbounded durations\n- Custom easing curves (only presets)\n\nAt billion-agent scale, unbounded animations cause resource exhaustion.\nThis editor guarantees all animations terminate.\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Render motion editor.\n\nShows sliders for duration, delay, iterations plus dropdowns for easing\nand direction. All values are bounded.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","ContextMenu","MotionEditor"],"MotionEditorProp"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element","Types"],"Element"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"visibility":"TypeVarInvisible"},"tag":"ForAll"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[303,74],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/ContextMenu/MotionEditor.purs","start":[303,1]},"title":"motionEditor"},{"children":[],"comments":"Animation state for 